Introduction
The Karakoram Range, known for its geopolitical and environmental significance, served as the focal point for this weather forecasting project. The objective was to leverage three decades of ground station temperature data to forecast weather patterns for the next 30 years. Advanced statistical and machine learning models, including LSTM, were employed to provide comprehensive insights into the climatic future of the Karakoram Range.

