Results
The model achieved a Mean Squared Error (MSE) of 0.006 and an R-squared (R2 score) of 0.835, indicating satisfactory predictive performance.

Future predictions for temperature trends in the Karakoram Range for the next 10 years have been generated and saved as CSV files.

